    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <p>
      This project is a dynamic MVC coffee shop management system.
      It is designed to help manage customer orders, menu items, and sales data.
      The system includes fully functional CRUD operations, interactive charts,
      and a chatbot to simulate real customer interactions in a coffee shop environment.
    </p>

    <h2>Logical Data Model</h2>
    <p>
      The data model supports the structure of the coffee shop system by organizing
      customers, orders, menu items, and order details. One customer can place many
      orders, and each order can include multiple items. Menu items can also appear
      in many different orders, forming one-to-many relationships within the system.
    </p>

